summaries.short: Spencer tries to broker peace; Charles struggles to deliver bad news; Joe attends a party at Andre's; Ricky is thrown for a loop by his dad.
summaries.full: Spencer attempts to broker peace between Travis and a critic. Struggling to adjust to his new role on the team, Charles is tasked with delivering some bad news. Joe encounters Andre one on one. Still torn about his future, Ricky is thrown for a loop when Dennis decides to have more of a voice in Ricky's life.

Ricky encourages Charles to stand up for himself; later, he gets some advice on a big career decision after running into a face from his past.
